{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ed1f5b54f3","title":"在鲁迅艺术文学院的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e57c0b8070","index":0,"year":1942,"month":5,"day":30,"articleId":"ed1f5b54f3"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3536ec6b1f","type":"paragraph","text":"在鲁迅艺术文学院的讲话“","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"ed1f5b54f3"},{"id":"894cf17b77","type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年5月30日）提高要以普及为基础，不要不起普及的东西，大树也是从像豆芽菜一样小的树苗长起来的。那些不起普及的人，他们在豆芽菜面前熟视无暗，结果把豆芽菜随便踩掉了。你们现在学习的地方是小鲁艺，还有一个大鲁艺，还要到大鲁艺去学习。大鲁艺就是工农兵群众的生活和斗争，广大的劳动人民就是大鲁艺的老师。你们应当认真地向他们学习，改造自己的思想感情，把自己的立足点逐步移到工农兵这一边来，才能成为真正的革命文艺工作者","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"ed1f5b54f3"}],"page":{"id":"7544e13df7","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"ed1f5b54f3","start":79,"end":79}}}},"__N_SSG":true}